Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.db

Class UncheckedConnection

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.db.UncheckedConnection
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, Connection, Wrapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
DatabaseEngine.Connection
public class UncheckedConnection
extends Object
implements Connection
A connection that guarantees to not throw SQLException from many of its methods. Such exceptions are wrapped as DataAccessExceptions instead.
Author:
Donal Fellows
